    <title type="html"><![CDATA[svn结合apache配置]]></title>
    <link href="http://lmj921.github.com/blog/2013/04/01/svnjie-he-apachepei-zhi/"/>
    <updated>2013-04-01T16:03:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://lmj921.github.com/blog/2013/04/01/svnjie-he-apachepei-zhi</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>记录下自己的svn配置，我直接使用的是windows版本的WANDisco SVN，如果是linux的话配置文件是类似的</p>

<p>httpd.conf文件，用于整合apache和svn</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt; KeepAlive On    &lt;Location /svn&gt;       DAV svn         SVNParentPath "d:/repositories"     AuthzSVNAccessFile d:/repositories/authz        AuthType Basic          AuthName "Subversion repos"         AuthUserFile d:/repositories/passwd         Require valid-user  &lt;/Location&gt; &lt;/VirtualHost&gt;
</span><span class='line'>```
</span><span class='line'>passwd文件，存放了每个用户的登录信息
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>1. 切换到apache/bin目录下
</span><span class='line'>2. 执行**htpasswd passwd username**
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>authz文件，用于控制权限
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>[groups]admin = design = dev = cdev = art = [/]@admin = rw[Design:/]<em> = r@admin = rw@design = rw[Art:/]</em> = r@admin = rw@design = r@art = rw[Server:/]@admin = rw@dev = rw[Client:/]@admin = rw@dev = rw@cdev = rw
&#8220;`</p>
